---
title: Spicy Harissa Chicken & Barley Bowl with Zucchini, Golden Raisins, Spicy Herb Sauce & Lemon Yogurt
description: Barley, with its chewy texture and nutty flavor, is an ancient grain that remains a favorite. In these spicy veggie bowls, our chefs opted for quick-cooking pearled barley as a hearty base for harissa-roasted zucchini, bell pepper, and onion. A spicy herb sauce and lemon yogurt are drizzled over top, then everything’s sprinkled with feta, toasted almonds, and golden raisins.
